videos.description: Maryland's Kevin Huerter lobs an alley-oop pass to Damonte Dodd who finishes with a dunk.
videos.headline: Dodd gets set up for an alley-oop slam

videos.description: Iowa's Peter Jok forces a turnover from Maryland's Anthony Cowan and he dunks it at the other end.
videos.headline: Peter Jok gets a steal and a dunk

videos.description: Iowa's Jordan Bohannon finds Ahmad Wagner in the paint and he makes the and-one basket to cut the Maryland lead to 7 points.
videos.headline: Great bounce pass sets up an and-one bucket for Iowa

videos.description: Iowa's Nicholas Baer gets a steal and Jordan Bohannon knocks down a three to tie the game at 66-66.
videos.headline: Iowa ties the game off a Maryland turnover

videos.description: Tied up at 72-72 with less than three minutes left on the clock, Maryland's Melo Trimble drains a 3-pointer to give the Terrapins the lead. Maryland would hold on to defeat Iowa 84-76.
videos.headline: Trimble's 3-pointer gives Maryland late lead

videos.description: Postgame Breakdown of Maryland's 84-76 win against Iowa.
videos.headline: Breaking down Melo Trimble's performance in the 2nd half of Maryland's 84-76 victory over Iowa

videos.description: Melo Trimble scores 20 points, five rebounds and five assists as No. 25 Maryland pulls away from Iowa late to win 84-76.
videos.headline: Trimble's 20 points fuel Maryland's win over Iowa
